page.title: 11Sand Dune Flora.
page.content:
320 plant species have been recorded on this lime poor dune system. The north east tip is covered with { {Sea lyme Grass}(Elymus arenarius) on the embryo dunes and as we go west across the dunes towards the forest the flora keeps changing. There is Sea lyme grass near the sea followed by Sea lyme grass and{lichen},followed by Sea lyme grass with lichen and{Rose {Bay Willow Herb.}Behind the dune in the wetter areas{Dwarf Willow, {Cats-ears,Bridsfoot Trefoil}appear. There is some fresh water fen,{Birch} and Alder are growing in the west and south of this area.
